            :class => "facebook-like-button",
            :frameborder => "0",
            :style => "border:none; overflow:scroll; width:120px; height:21px;",
            :allowTransparency => "true"}
  %h2 Coming Soon
  %p
    Register your interest now and get special behind the scenes access and free message credits when we launch beta.
